    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561544>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Micraster ernsti sp. nov. A, pore pairs in anterior aboral ambulacrum (paratype MB.E.8583, conica/pappilosa Zone, lower Campanian, Teutonia Nord quarry). B, adapical ambulacrum (petal IV) (MB.E.8576, paratype, conica/ pappilosa Zone, lower Campanian, Höver quarry). C, parafascioles is indicated by arrows (MB.E. 8576, paratype). D, peristomal area, with plastronal plates and periplastronal ambulacrals (MB.E.8577, holotype, conica/pappilosa Zone, lower Campanian, Höver quarry)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561544/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561546>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Micraster ernsti sp. nov. A, plate drawing of the oral surface (MB.E.8583, paratype, conica/pappilosa Zone, lower Campanian, Teutonia Nord quarry). B, plate drawing of the oral surface (MB.E.8577, holotype conica/ pappilosa Zone, lower Campanian, Höver quarry); MB.E.13284). C, plate drawing of the apical disc (MB.E.8583, paratype, conica/pappilosa Zone, lower Campanian, Teutonia Nord quarry). Fractures were neglected in the drawings." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561546/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

